body.name: TCL 10 Plus Unlocked Smartphone, 6.47” Curved AMOLED FHD+ Display, Verizon Cellphone 6/64GB with 48MP Rear AI Quad-Camera, 4500mAh Fast Charging Battery, OTG Reverse Charging, Starlight Silver
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Wednesday, February 14. Order within 14 hrs 50 mins
features: 【Compatible】This device is certified for use on Verizon’s LTE network. If your device experiences an error when making phone calls on Verizon, your account may need to be provisioned to support “CDMA-less” devices. Please contact Verizon’s technical support team or your account’s business representative for assistance. This device is not compatible with CDMA and GSM networks.(such as AT&T, T-Mobile, Sprint, Spectrum, Xfinity,etc.)

【Experience Infinite Immersion with Display】Experience infinite immersion with TCL 10 Plus’ 6.47-inch FHD+ curved AMOLED display powered by NXTVISION visual technology. Endlessly smooth bezel-free design and 3D front glass provide you durable, sleek device in celestial colors. Masterfully manage your device using intelligent power features, easy file transferring and a customizable UI. This display provides unending views with 93% screen-to-body ratio with perfect details anywhere any time.

【Intelligent AI Quad-Camera】TCL 10 Plus features a 48MP high-res camera with AI scene-detection algorithm. The main camera lets you capture sharp resolution and detail while identifying and enhancing scenes and objects to create the highest quality image possible. The world is yours to capture with a 48MP AI Quad-Camera capable of shooting in extreme lighting conditions.

【Powerful Big Battery&18W Fast Charging】TCL 10 Plus features a powerful 4500mAh big battery. The phone supports 18W (9V2A) QC3.0 fast charging which can charge up to 50% in 40 minutes.And it also features 5V1A OTG reverse charging to power up headsets, wearables and other phones.

【Fingerprint-on-display】TCL 10 Plus’ hidden in-display optical scanner gives the phone a smooth, sleek profile. It detects and creates the fingerprint image by determining the light and dark areas created by the fingerprint ridges. Simply tap the screen of your phone to unlock it in just 0.3 seconds.

【Super Bluetooth】Thanks to TCL 10 Plus’s Super Bluetooth multi-streaming audio solution, users can connect up to 4 Bluetooth speakers to amplify audio experience; or pair with up to 4 Bluetooth headphones to multi-share the music with friends.

【Internal Storage】The phone's 64GB memory allows you to store and access all the photos, videos, music, books and files you need instantly without worrying about running out of space. You can also add up to 256GB of memory with a microSD card (sold separately).

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 48MP high-res AI camera TCL 10 Plus features a 48MP high-res camera with AI scene-detection algorithm. The main camera lets you capture sharp resolution and detail while identifying and enhancing scenes and objects to create the highest quality image possible. Up to 3 times brighter night shots in extreme low-light scenarios with innovative algorithm that integrates Auto-brightness, Denoising, Super Resolution, HDR and more into a single AI model. Super Night Mode Make nightscapes like none other with Super Night Mode. Maximizing your night photography in a breeze with a dedicated Super Night Mode. When the mode is turned on, the device shoots eight photos in four seconds, compressing them into a single photo with sharper detail and less noise. Super wide-angle camera In comparison to usual standard camera angle (74°), the 118° super wide-angle camera can capture about 3.3*times more content in a single shot, helping the users to create a more professional like photo/video with better composition and accurate perspective. Include the landscape, skyline or friends in full excellence with an AI algorithm without any distortion.

Netflix HDR10 streaming supported Rigorously tested with a variety of scenes in bright and dark environments for HDR picture quality, brightness, contrast and color accuracy tone mapping, TCL 10 Plus ensures users always enjoy incredible viewing as the directors intended. 4-in-1 big pixel low-light selfie Brighter self-portraits in low-light conditions with 16MP selfie camera. 4-in-1 big pixel binning technology automatically merges 4 small 1.0μm pixels into a big 2.0μm pixel to provide twice the light, which results in brighter selfies. Qualcomm Snapdragon 665 AI Engine Effortless multitasking with heightened performance and lower power use thanks to 11nm processing technology. Lightning-fast experiences for great mobile gaming, brilliant camera capabilities and remarkable, security-rich performance.

TCL 10L - NXTVISION Display Take visual power to the limit with TCL 10 Plus’ bezel-free 6.47-inch FHD+ curved AMOLED display powered by a dedicated display engine. NXTVISION visual technology with visual and HDR enhancement create color, detail and contrast at their most compelling, with viewing modes for excellent visuals in any environment. Reach for the stars with TCL 10 Plus' celestial-inspired colors that provide subtle shine, sleek 3D front glass and perfectly aligned features for eye-pleasing symmetry. Experience the powerhouse performance of TCL 10 Plus. A long-lasting 4500mAh battery and array of intelligent power management features maximize your power so you can go all day long. Multitasking is easier than ever with a Qualcomm Snapdragon 665 AI Engine that powers up performance while preserving your battery. Store all the photos, music and more you can't live without in a 6GB + 64GB memory. Enjoy effortless connectivity with powerfully portable Super Bluetooth audio sharing and wireless file management. Accessing what you need has never been more instant with the intuitive TCL UI equipped with customizable shortcuts and an Always-On Display. Technical Parameters: HD Voice Lens: 6P + 5P + 3P + 3P Aperture: F1.8 + F2.2 + F2.4 + F2.4 Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 665 Speed & Type: Qualcomm Kyro 260 octa-core processor RAM+ROM: 6GB+64GB, GPU: Adreno 610, Weight: 6.07oz/ 172g Dimensions: 6.26” x 2.87” x 0.35” / 158.9 x 72.88 x 8.95mm

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Buy this phone now
reviews.reviewText: The value you get for the price is uncomparable to any phone I've ever had in my entire life. It is packed with features that rival a flagship phone worth over $1,000. It doesn't have the best processor or the most memory but it does have an SD card slot which is perfect Since most phones don't have that feature anymore. The screen is amazing the build quality is top notch and I'm thinking about getting one for myself because I got this one for my girlfriend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I definitely recommend!
reviews.reviewText: My bf and I both have 1 and it is a GREAT phone! Long battery,loud speaker and the camera quality it beautiful

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty good budget phone
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my little boy and I am very impressed for the price. It has a pretty darn good display to start, which is very vivid. The OS is pretty snappy for having an older snapdragon processor (with some developmental tweaks to animation scales). For a $120, it's a good quality phone! Minus a star only because I have a S23ultra to compare.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars update! Bad screen x2 TCL is my new BLU!
reviews.reviewText: Update, after 2 months of use, screen seems to be bleeding tie-dye colors that interact with the touch functions, actually purchased three of these for the family and two out of the three have defective screens, very disappointed cannot recommendAwesome specs for the price. on-screen fingerprint sensor does take some getting used to,but is ultimately almost as snappy as a dedicated sensor. Phone feels very premium, and AMOLED screen is great! I worried that the curved edges would make it feel lesss solid in my grip, but its not an issue.FYI: this phone DOES come with a clear TPU case. I was confused about this, and ordered a case that now will cost be half of its price to return... I used to purchase BLU branded phones for their great spec/price ratio but last year Straight Talk switched to VoLTE for its GSM service and did not whitelist BLU. Straight Talk ended up sending my wife and I the LOWEST of low end phones as " free" replacements, but these were unusably crappy. TCL to the rescue! Got this model for $119 on sale, but if I had paid the full price of $159, I dont think id have been disappointed. If only the product description more clearly explained the inclusion of a case... :-)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So far so good
reviews.reviewText: There's no issues with the device but there is an issue with screen protectors they don't fit other than that if you're looking for a case there is also an issue if you're looking for them on Amazon they're coming from China like everything else but I haven't received my case it's gotten lost in the mail supposedly from China I ordered another one we'll see if that one makes it but the device works flawlessly so 100% for that it comes with a case already in the box and the charger and everything but I wanted a different case and it's hard to get those

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 27, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars The charging port will not except the charging cord
reviews.reviewText: I love the phone . It makes beautiful photos and videos. The problem is , it can not be charged. The port on the bottom will not recieve the charging plug. The good thing is Amazon is sending me a new phone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I don't regret a second having purchased this phone. Very good, battery life is great. Overall zero drama. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023

reviews.reviewText: Costo y calidad excelente, llegó antes de tiempo, tengo 15 días con el y funciona a la perfección, es fluid en las aplicaciones y su pantalla genial.
Hasta ahora el celular a rendido muy bien es rápido me gusta mucho sus cámaras tengo junto con el un tcl 10se y su marca es muy buena.

Pues me gustó, muy buena pantalla, algo fragil, un poco que desear con el sistema operativo y pues también en redes , vi que dicen que funciona con redes altan y la verdad no, solo funciona un momento y luego que no es compatible, funciona con Telcel y el sonido me parece bastante bueno si eres usuario Telcel y buscas algo decente y económico este puede ser el celular

reviews.reviewTitle: Gran teléfono por lo que cuesta
reviews.reviewText: Me gustó mucho su pantalla y su optimización, no conocía la marca tcl en teléfonos, pero es una grata sorpresa, al menos este modelo porque funciona muy bienNo me gusta que no funcionó el cubo del cargador y la publicidad, ya que no existe el color lavanda en este modelo, es gris plata y otra cosa que no me gusta es que no hay fundas protectoras ni vidrios templados para la protección de la pantalla, ya que no es un modelo para el mercado americano ni para el europeo, fue un modelo exclusivo para Asia

reviews.reviewTitle: Por el precio compraría uno más
reviews.reviewText: La pantalla es de un teléfono de gama alta ,y las fotos que logras capturar son de buena calidad,no es un teléfono que se caracteriza por tener cámaras de excelente resolución,pero son buenas, y el rendimiento es aceptable
